---
import ToolLayout from '../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "What is the Amazon Associates program?",
    answer: "Amazon Associates is Amazon's affiliate marketing program. It allows website owners, bloggers, and content creators to monetize their traffic by placing affiliate tracking links that earn commission whenever a reader makes a purchase."
  },
  {
    question: "How do product categories affect my commission rates?",
    answer: "Amazon uses fixed commission rates based on the category of the item purchased. E.g., Luxury Beauty offers a high 10% rate; Books, Kitchen, and Automotive offer 4.5%; whereas PC/Electronics offer 2.5%, and Kindle/Tablets offer 1%."
  },
  {
    question: "What is a typical Amazon affiliate conversion rate?",
    answer: "Because Amazon is a highly trusted marketplace with Prime shipping benefits, conversion rates are generally high compared to standard e-commerce, typically averaging between 3% and 8% depending on audience search intent."
  },
  {
    question: "What is the Amazon 24-hour cookie window?",
    answer: "When a reader clicks your Amazon affiliate link, a tracking cookie is placed in their browser. You earn a commission on any products they add to their cart within 24 hours. The cookie expires once they submit their order or after 24 hours."
  }
];
---

<ToolLayout
  title="Amazon Affiliate Earnings Calculator - Commission Estimator"
  description="Calculate your Amazon Associates affiliate earnings. Free online commission calculator with official Amazon category rates, clicks, and conversion inputs."
  toolName="Amazon Affiliate Calculator"
  toolDescription="Estimate your Amazon Associates income. Input your traffic clicks, choose product categories to auto-fill official commission rates, and review yearly earnings projections."
  category="Calculators"
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <div slot="calculator" class="calc-card glass">
    <div class="calc-grid" id="calc-form-container">
      <!-- Input fields -->
      <form class="calc-form" id="amazon-form" onsubmit="return false;">
        <div class="form-row-2">
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="label-header">
              <label for="monthly-clicks" class="icon-label">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="field-icon">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.042 9.152c.582.448 1.148.89 1.676 1.345m-8.364-.347c-.528-.456-1.094-.898-1.676-1.345M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707m12.728 0l-.707-.707M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364-6.364l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707m12.728 0l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707M15 12a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" />
                </svg>
                Monthly Link Clicks
              </label>
            </div>
            <input type="number" id="monthly-clicks" class="form-input" placeholder="e.g., 5000" min="1" step="1" required />
          </div>

          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="label-header">
              <label for="item-price" class="icon-label">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="field-icon">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
                </svg>
                Average Item Price ($)
              </label>
            </div>
            <input type="number" id="item-price" class="form-input" placeholder="e.g., 35" min="1" step="0.01" required />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-row-2">
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="label-header">
              <label for="product-category" class="icon-label">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="field-icon">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.568 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 5.25v4.318c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591l9.581 9.581a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 1.591 0l4.318-4.318a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 0-1.591L9.568 3.659A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 7.977 3Z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 7.5h.008v.008H6V7.5Z" />
                </svg>
                Product Category
              </label>
            </div>
            <select id="product-category" class="form-input">
              <option value="4.5" selected>Books, Kitchen, Automotive (4.50%)</option>
              <option value="10.0">Luxury Beauty, Luxury Stores (10.00%)</option>
              <option value="5.0">Digital Music, Digital Video, Handmade (5.00%)</option>
              <option value="4.0">Apparel, Shoes, Jewelry, Luggage (4.00%)</option>
              <option value="3.0">Home, Lawn & Garden, Pets, Toys (3.00%)</option>
              <option value="2.5">PC, PC Components, DVD, Blu-Ray (2.50%)</option>
              <option value="2.0">Televisions, Digital Video Games (2.00%)</option>
              <option value="1.0">Tablets, Kindle, Ring, Video Games (1.00%)</option>
              <option value="custom">Custom Commission Rate Override...</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="form-group" id="custom-rate-box" style="display: none;">
            <div class="label-header">
              <label for="custom-commission" class="icon-label">Custom Commission (%)</label>
            </div>
            <input type="number" id="custom-commission" class="form-input" placeholder="e.g., 4.5" min="0.1" max="50" step="0.1" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <div class="label-header">
            <label for="conversion-rate" class="icon-label">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="field-icon">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.34 18.062 18 21m-2.66-2.938a7.478 7.478 0 0 0 1.256-4.242A7.472 7.472 0 0 0 9 6.25a7.472 7.472 0 0 0-7.592 7.57 7.461 7.461 0 0 0 1.256 4.242L0 21m15.34-2.938A7.476 7.476 0 0 0 16.5 13.75c0-4.14-3.36-7.5-7.5-7.5h-.012c-4.137 0-7.488 3.353-7.488 7.47a7.473 7.473 0 0 0 1.156 3.968l1.455-1.597a5.525 5.525 0 0 1-.611-2.371c0-3.053 2.477-5.529 5.525-5.529h.012c3.048 0 5.525 2.476 5.525 5.53a5.523 5.523 0 0 1-.611 2.37l1.455 1.598Z" />
              </svg>
              Conversion Rate (%)
            </label>
          </div>
          <input type="number" id="conversion-rate" class="form-input" placeholder="e.g., 5" min="0.1" max="50" step="0.1" value="5.0" required />
          <span class="input-helper">The percentage of link clicks that buy (Amazon Associate average is 3% - 8%).</span>
        </div>

        <div class="form-actions">
          <button type="button" id="calc-submit-btn" class="calc-btn" style="width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" style="width: 18px; height: 18px;">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
            </svg>
            Calculate Affiliate Earnings
          </button>
          <button type="button" id="calc-reset-btn" class="calc-btn-secondary" style="width: 100%;">Reset Form</button>
        </div>
      </form>

      <!-- Outputs Display -->
      <div class="calc-results" id="results-wrapper">
        <div class="empty-state text-center" id="res-empty-box">
          <svg class="empty-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 6a7.5 7.5 0 1 0 7.5 7.5h-7.5V6Z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 10.5H21A7.5 7.5 0 0 0 13.5 3v7.5Z" />
          </svg>
          <h3>Awaiting Click Metrics</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Enter your monthly affiliate link traffic to calculate commission distributions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="results-active hidden" id="res-active-box">
          <div class="rate-range-box">
            <h4 class="rate-label">Est. Monthly Earnings</h4>
            <div class="rate-range" id="res-earnings-val">$0.00</div>
            <div class="grade-badge grade-low" id="res-range-val">$0 - $0 range</div>
          </div>

          <div class="breakdown-box">
            <h4 class="breakdown-title">Commission Metrics Audit</h4>
            <div class="breakdown-list">
              <div class="breakdown-item">
                <span class="breakdown-label">Total Monthly Clicks:</span>
                <span class="breakdown-val" id="res-clicks-val">-</span>
              </div>
              <div class="breakdown-item">
                <span class="breakdown-label">Calculated Items Sold:</span>
                <span class="breakdown-val" id="res-items-val">-</span>
              </div>
              <div class="breakdown-item">
                <span class="breakdown-label">Gross Sales volume:</span>
                <span class="breakdown-val" id="res-gross-val">-</span>
              </div>
              <div class="breakdown-item">
                <span class="breakdown-label">Projected Yearly Income:</span>
                <span class="breakdown-val" id="res-yearly-val" style="color: var(--color-brand); font-weight: 700;">-</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div slot="about">
    <h2>How to Use This Amazon Affiliate Calculator</h2>
    <p>
      Monetizing a blog or niche site through Amazon Associates requires calculating click values. Since Amazon commissions are structured strictly by category, this **amazon associate calculator** streamlines rate projections.
    </p>

    <div style="margin: 1.5rem 0; background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-brand);">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem;">
        💡 <strong>Want a detailed breakdown of commission rules?</strong> Read our comprehensive guide on <a href="/blog/amazon-affiliate-calculator-guide" style="color: var(--color-brand); text-decoration: underline;">Amazon Affiliate Commission Rates & Calculation Strategies</a> to learn cookie window rules, conversion optimizations, and category payouts.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="step-guide">
      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 1: Enter Monthly Link Clicks</h3>
        <p>Input the number of clicks your affiliate links generate per month. You can extract this from your Google Analytics or the Amazon Associates reporting dashboard.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 2: Choose Product Category</h3>
        <p>Select your product category from the dropdown to auto-fill the corresponding commission rate. If you promote custom bounty offers or have special contract terms, select <strong>Custom Commission</strong> to override.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 3: Define Average Selling Price (ASP)</h3>
        <p>Enter the average price of the items purchased by your readers. If you write review articles for budget kitchen gadgets, this might be $25. For high-end PC hardware, this could be $200.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 4: Pick a Conversion Rate</h3>
        <p>Enter your conversion rate. A standard starting baseline is 5%. If your review articles target users with high purchasing intent (e.g. 'best kitchen knives' reviews), your conversion rate may range from 8% to 12%.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Features & Projections</h2>
    <p>
      The **amazon affiliate income calculator** is equipped with several features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Official Category Rate Mapping:</strong> Automatically applies official Amazon Associates commission percentages based on your selections.</li>
      <li><strong>Gross Volume Valuation:</strong> Tracks the total sales volume ($) you generate for Amazon's e-commerce ecosystem.</li>
      <li><strong>Yearly Income Projections:</strong> Multiplies monthly commissions by 12 to provide long-term income forecasting.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Benefits of Projecting Affiliate Earnings</h2>
    <p>
      Auditing your traffic value provides key operational benefits:
    </p>
    <ol style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">
      <li><strong>Auditing Niche Viability:</strong> Calculates earnings *before* you invest months into launching a new website, letting you identify high-paying product categories.</li>
      <li><strong>Establishing Conversion Targets:</strong> Helps you model how small increases in conversion rate or Average Selling Price (ASP) impact monthly revenue.</li>
      <li><strong>Optimizing Monetization:</strong> If click earnings are low, it can help you evaluate switching from Amazon Associates to high-paying direct brand sponsorships.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
</ToolLayout>

<style>
  /* Enforce rounded corners on the entire tool card and give it clean outer padding */
